The paper discusses the development of a mathematical model for safety assurance in self-driving cars, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). Additionally, the paper proposes a design for a scalable system, which involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI), control systems (cs.SY), software engineering (cs.SE), and machine learning (cs.LG).
